Sensor Alignment Principle

A good multimedia answer aligns every human learning channel:

Words explain.
Voice emphasizes.
Images anchor.
Motion shows causality.
Music controls energy.
Captions reinforce memory.
Timing creates comprehension.
Interaction enables depth.

This is the all-sensors-aligned output model.

